I wish I'd read ALL the reviews before making this recipe. Right now I agree with most tips: set the dish aside before baking for a little while if using frozen dough & use a food processor; cook longer than the recommended 30-40 minutes or the center will be too soft; reduce the butter - it literally swims in liquid fat on the way to the cool down phase. Otherwise delicious.

